snippet.title: LAURE X EKDEV LIMBU - TIHAR SONG [OFFICIAL VIDEO 2025] | KABITA NEPALI
snippet.description:
Actually, I created this song long time ago but whenever I listen to it, I felt something incomplete and I thought that I could do lot of experiments to make this song more close towards the perfection. This year, finally, with the help, courage and push from my beloved people I am able to present you guys this beautiful masterpiece. 

â€œTIHAR SONGâ€ is an occasional song but if you dissect this creation musically and visually, you can find lots of interesting things, which will make your normal days; lightened and brighten up like Tihar. Happy Tihar to you all. May goddess Laxmi bless you and your family with wealth and good health. Jay Nepal ğŸ‡³ğŸ‡µ

snippet.title: Baahubali - The Epic Release Trailer (Hindi) | Prabhas, Rana | SS Rajamouli | 31st October2025
snippet.description:
#BaahubaliTheEpic is a combined narrative of the two-part Indian film saga, weaving together the grandeur and drama of Baahubali: The Beginning and Baahubali: The Conclusion into one epic tale.

CAST:
Prabhas as Sivudu & Baahubali, Rana Daggubati as Bhallaladeva, Anushka Shetty as Devasena, Tamannaah as Avanthika with Ramya Krishna, Nasser, Sathyaraj, Kiccha Sudeepa, Adivi Sesh, Rakesh Varre, Meka Ramakrishna.

CREW:
Screenplay & Direction: S.S. Rajamouli
Presented by: K. Raghavendra Rao B.A.
Producers: Shobu Yarlagadda & Prasad Devineni
Story: VV Prasad
DOP: K.K. Senthil Kumar
Production Designer: Sabu Cyril
Music Composer: M.M. Keeravaani
VFX Supervision: V. Srinivas Mohan
Sound Design: P.M. Satheesh
Stunt Choreography: Peter Hein
Additional Stunts: King Solomon, Lee Whittakar, Kaloyan Vodenicharov
Dance Choreographers: Prem Rakshit, Shankar, Dinesh Kumar, Jani
Editor: Tammiraju
Costume Designer: Rama Rajamouli, Prashanti Tripirneni
Dialogues:
Telugu - C.H. Vijay Kumar, Ajay Kumar G
Hindi - Manoj Muntashir

snippet.title: Spirit Prabhas Teaser REVIEW | Deeksha Sharma
snippet.description:
Spirit Prabhas Teaser Review By Deeksha Sharma. Spirit Announcement by Sandeep Reddy Vanga Starring Prabhas & Triptii Dimri is the Next Big Thing after Animal Ranbir Kapoor Box Office Success. SPIRIT - OneBadHabit Teaser Trailer introduces Prabhas like never before with Dark Police Story based around Don Lee Rumours & Vivek Oberoi as the New Villain. Spirit Prabhas Announcement Reaction & Full Movie Expectations would be shared in this Video. Can Sandeep Reddy Vanga Score big like Animal or Prabhas Stardom would be too hard to handle? Do leave Comments below.

#Spirit #SpiritPrabhas #SpiritTeaser

     https://www.instagram.com/thefilmiindian

id.description:
Film iklan terbesar dan terpedas tahun ini telah HADIR!
Atlee x Ranveer Singh berkolaborasi dengan Sreeleela & Bobby Deol untuk ledakan sinematik terliar yang memadukan aksi, drama, komedi, & masala.

Tonton trailer AGENT CHING ATTACKS yang eksplosif dengan aksi yang memukau, drama yang memukau, musik yang menghentak, dan masala yang begitu panas... akan membakar semangat Anda.

Film lengkapnya tayang perdana Minggu, 19 Oktober, eksklusif di kanal ini.

APA YANG HARUS DIHARAPKAN:
â€¢ Ranveer Singh dalam avatar terkuatnya sebagai Agen Ching
â€¢ Sreeleela menambahkan bumbu dan gaya sebagai Agen Mirchi
â€¢ Bobby Deol melepaskan kekacauan sebagai Profesor White Noise
â€¢ Skala, gaya, & tontonan khas Atlee dengan kru papan atas dunia
â€¢ Versi baru dari lagu kebangsaan ikonik "My Name is Ranveer Ching"

Dari Bhatinda hingga Beijing, hanya ada satu rajaâ€¦ Ranveer Ching!

Ini adalah perayaan TERBESAR untuk orang Tionghoa Desi â€” berani, penuh cita rasa, sinematik, dan dijamin #AagLagaDe.

Tentang Rahasia Ching - Konon untuk memenangkan hati orang Hindustan, bahkan makanan Tionghoa pun menjadi desi! Dan hanya ada satu merek makanan Tionghoa Desi yang dapat membuat hati orang desi berdebar lebih kencang â€“ Ching's. Berkuah. Pedas. Manis asam. Panas asam. Renyah. Slurpy. Segar. Schezwani. Manchuriaâ€¦ Apa pun jenis masakan Tionghoa Desi yang Anda idamkan, hanya Ching yang bisa memuaskan selera Anda dengan rasa yang sempurna.

Saya â™¥ Tionghoa Desi!

snippet.title: Rs 50000 Minecraft DeathSwap Challenge with a YouTuber!
snippet.description:
Rs 50000 Minecraft DeathSwap Challenge with a YouTuber!


Instagram pe 50k kar do: https://www.instagram.com/psd_1/

In this video, I do a Minecraft deathswap challenge with my YouTuber friend @MrLapis 
where we both get 15 mins to build traps for each other, and as the timer finishes, our position gets swapped with each other. The player who survives in the end wins and gets Rs 50000!

snippet.title: Ujan Shakya - Baby (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
MEY STUDIO & VISIONS MEDIA PRODUCTION
PRESENTS

BABY by Ujan Shakya || New Newari Song || New Nepal Bhasa Song || New Nepali Song

"Baby" explores the theme of love. It depicts the concept of love at first sight through a narrative that combines imagination and emotion. The piece is characterized as an emotional afrobeat , featuring a blend of Newari instruments.


Written, Music Produced & Performed by : UJAN SHAKYA
